## 9. Conclusion

This paper has proposed and verified the CTRA architecture. Engineering verification demonstrates that the DIEA conjugate dual-ring possesses real-time tampering detection, isolation, and self-healing capabilities; the Fourth Wall Protocol achieves efficient asymmetric interaction; the tri-ring empathy architecture realizes endogenous affective experience, cognitive reappraisal, and cross-stage meta-insight; and the causal world state machine can restore balance through homeostasis after extreme impacts. CTRA provides an underlying topological paradigm for the secure and controllable development of AGI.

